							The most obvious way to use Happnin is when you want to find
							something to do or somewhere to go. There is nothing easier than
							that: pull up the app, and you will be presented with a list of
							restaurants / cafes / clubs or bars around you (this list comes
							from the biggest database of venues available as of today: Yelp !)
							. From there, you can easily look up the feed of tweets or
							Instagram posts relative to this place, to get a feel of what is
							going on there. Besides, you can easily get directions to go there
							or call the place to make a reservation in two seconds.
						</p>
						<br>
